=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_BRZ2_ex2 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright mixed sound, with complex oscillator character around 52 Hz, featuring punchy attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: mixed
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 52.0666
  harmonic_decay_rate: -0.0273
  harmonic_regularity: 0.1622
  pitch_clarity: 9.0697
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -3.8451
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

